Password Safe is a password manager. It stores your passwords in an
encrypted file, allowing you to remember only one password "master
password", instead of all the username/password combinations that you use.

Password Safe is a cross-platform password manager compatible with the
Password Safe v3 database format. This port packages the wxWidgets GUI
application, as well as a command-line utility `pwsafe-cli`.

Note: the GUI executable is installed as `pwsafe-gui` to avoid conflicting
with the existing pwsafe and pwsafe-nox11 command-line ports.
